{"tid":2323783,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解有啲男人只會用大隻黎打飛機？","createTime":"2020-12-13T12:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T02:18:06.000Z","uid":254745,"like":16,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5dbfb2daccf7bf6b2cbd4e9c10143ce38e0e79db","tid":2323783,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"最近成為左gym撚，見到有啲傻仔用大隻黎打飛機，用黎食女就覺得好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男人由始至終得三樣野代表佢優秀既DNA：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 讀到書(學歷)<br />\n2. 身高<br />\n<br />\n3. 錢（最好先天藍血有家底嗰種，其次用1. 搵到錢，證明到自己既能力）<br />\n<br />\n大隻呢啲有得後天操返黎既野，係差在你操唔操，都用黎打Ｊ真係笑撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然你如果有齊1+2+3，再加埋大隻就梗係更加好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個有返少少質素既女人根本就只會care個男你係咪smart，啲有錢男人搵另一半就係好好例子，娶返黎既一定有學歷，玩女人就另外。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可能話咁代表操大隻可以食到女，屌西啫過人世咩，<br />\n咪撚玩啦，啲女見你戇鳩鳩咁，連屌都唔想俾你屌啦，<br />\n至少我讀U啲中上女係咁，都費時俾你啲垃圾DNA污染。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n地盤佬夠大隻，倉佬夠大隻啦，又有幾多女人鍾意呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：有齊1+2+一半3+大隻"},{"pid":"135725e95e5208e71f2e82d3543e0ee1b2623710","tid":2323783,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:28:13.000Z","msg":"地盤佬7成藍絲<br />\n物流倉業8成藍絲<br />\n<br />\n唔怕做例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d065e3ba88d3c71ed4612f65e40fb2fc4659d492","tid":2323783,"uid":362757,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:37:37.000Z","msg":"你有齊1 2 3 就唔會咁得閒開膠po la😂😂<br />\n秒左你sor😏"},{"pid":"7aeb29442d40b276277254fc781c8d0c93638e9d","tid":2323783,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"d065e3ba88d3c71ed4612f65e40fb2fc4659d492","tid":2323783,"uid":362757,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:37:37.000Z","msg":"你有齊1 2 3 就唔會咁得閒開膠po la😂😂<br />\n秒左你sor😏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:39:04.000Z","msg":"講中左你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n1,2好難有咩？"},{"pid":"f5b89911188d38a2796551c5e5bcc24542e519f4","tid":2323783,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067c4d93b9061c5716d997579a5d3e6a107d5552","tid":2323783,"uid":222938,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:45:45.000Z","msg":"翻譯：樓主唔夠人大隻俾人搶左條女，唯有用學歷同身高打飛機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5840bc081294a5eda717500cebd3239113d69ad","tid":2323783,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T12:50:17.000Z","msg":"地盤同倉佬個啲叫大隻咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪撈亂咗大力同大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a030858465b4527781b5593a87b10edea5d4dce","tid":2323783,"uid":53209,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T13:30:15.000Z","msg":"借問聲 你係咪生得好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a568fe537235d977d6117fbf69e4fa68d692ff3","tid":2323783,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"3a0